{"tid":1723790,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"罷工真係好 Q 正...","createTime":"2019-11-15T09:34:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-15T16:07:25.000Z","uid":15394,"like":42,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"e4d7a262784a7c6f131f8804b9775e29a5ce50be","tid":1723790,"uid":15394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T09:34:26.000Z","msg":"罷左五日工，起身慢慢食早餐, 睇住旁邊D西裝友趕頭趕命,自己懶懶飲杯奶茶 <br />\n<br />\n食完早餐, 返屋企上網睇live, 每日retweet 十幾個msg 差唔多, <br />\n<br />\n之後訓覺, 訓到十二點或者一點起身, 可以開電腦睇劇, 睇電影, 打下機, 有左電腦, 呢個世界大把免費娛樂 <br />\n<br />\n到左三四點, 可能會覺肚餓, 由於消耗唔多, 可以考慮落街10蚊兩個包, 或者 食麥皮 <br />\n<br />\nHEA到晚上, 如果有家人就返屋企食飯, 冇就盡可能自己煮, 節省少少 <br />\n<br />\n罷工罷左5日, 依照咁既生活方式, 扣除必要開支, 總支出大概平時返工四成左右, <br />\n<br />\n諗落都覺得好笑, 我辛苦工作, 為左就係六七十歲後, 可以享受類似咁既休閒寧靜既生活 <br />\n<br />\n原來罷工已經可以做到, 人生真係可笑, 哈哈"},{"pid":"171f72de5a5cd2ace4be61b023e75e668e74af7d","tid":1723790,"uid":15854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T09:36:41.000Z","msg":"哈哈"},{"pid":"da78603fd808f5e6529a01baa73ca1556e3b0a88","tid":1723790,"uid":15394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T09:36:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4085799404fa6c92e30ef21b18df73914f0c2f93","tid":1723790,"uid":87557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T09:36:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b36aa170996264a92a1e1d7356f4480a7ddd3eae","tid":1723790,"uid":76383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T09:38:16.000Z","msg":"哈哈"},{"pid":"5de5cefd2938cd5fa3b3f1ad4d7ca7b43fddd5c4","tid":1723790,"uid":182406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T09:38:51.000Z","msg":"哈哈"},{"pid":"39a05a95cd610f5f36c5a14cf1716d